item.title: An Analysis of Eminem Lyrics - NLP
item.description: This is a test post for my incoming blog, and a sneak peek to my first post. Given that it’s a test post, though, I reserve the right to write terribly. Eminem has been a phenomenon since The Slim Shady LP caught Dr. Dre’s ears. Throughout his career, Eminem has filled the airwaves with his thoughts and emotions. Here we perform an analysis on his lyrics in 2 parts.
